components.content: IMPORTANT NOTICE:  To comply with our policy documentation drafted by our legal counsel, your source of income and wealth needs to be commensurate (in proportion) with the information you have provided throughout this form and the value of your contribution.   For example, an employee with a low level of salary and no other sources of income/wealth or financing would be deemed to not be able to acquire a high cost asset which was clearly beyond his/her means.  Insufficient information provided here may result in your application not being approved or processed in time for the ICO.

components.content:
Examples of independent verification for "Salary/Earnings" include: (1) wage/salary receipt or slips issued by your employer; or (2) bank statements which reflect the payment of your salary (even if the name of the payer is not shown but the statements reflect a regular payment commensurate with the salary disclosed this will suffice); or (3) copy of employment contract which contains your yearly salary and employer's signature and details.
This list is not intended to be exhaustive.

Content
components.content: An example of independent verification of "Crypto Assets Trading" includes a snapshot of wallet timestamp of crypto acquired early on at low values.  Your application will not be approved or processed on time if it is not clear from the transaction(s) where you made your significant source of wealth.

Please upload independent verification for "Sale of Real Estate":
Content
components.content: Examples of independent verification for "Sale of Real Estate" include: (1) copy of deeds, contracts or other documents preferably notarised when public or in the event of private documents independently verified with counter party or professionals involved in the transaction; (2) or extract from land registry or equivalent reflecting value and date of transaction and parties.  This list is not intended to be an exhaustive.

components.label: Please provide a full explanation of the source of wealth gained from your "Sale of Real Estate":
Content
components.content: Examples of independent verification for "Gift/Inheritance" include: (1) copy of Will, Grant of Probate, Letters of Administration or equivalent where these reflect specific bequests or the value of the estate; or (2) written confirmation from executor, administrators or equivalent evidencing distributions made; or (3) deed or other document vesting assets bequeathed or gifted; or (4) written confirmation from Trustees or equivalent of the nature and value of the distributions made.   This list is not intended to be an exhaustive list.
